Text.SourceString: I run around the forest this morning. Its a great way to start my day..
Having a child changed my life, in a good way.. It gives life a whole new purpose.
I used to not care about my diet or lifestyle until I have Valentina. Then I become label reader momster. Haha
What do you have in agenda for the week Player?
Alice is obviously the soft-spoken one. Sometimes, I can barely hear what shes saying! She needs to speak up a bit.
Alice and I are twins. That much should be obvious ya.. But people do mistake us all the time.
No I cant read her mind. She also cant feel it when Im pinched. And no, we dont do everything together..
Working hard Player?
Im trying to take Valentina to school every morning, then I would jog back home..
If I dont take her to school now, when else will I be able to do that again..
Soon she will grow up, then off to university.. Time flies Player
Tofu ice cream is good. I love the texture
Diamond and pearls remind me of many happy memories.. They are my most favorite things..
Im Suki.. No problem. happens all the time.
I let Alice picks out our wine selection. I dont really care about alcohol..
My sister may look small to you, but boy can she eat!! Especially if you give her banana fritter
Im usually on desk duty from day to night on the weekend..
They have yoga class on Saturdays in the community center. A lot of people usually turned up..
I think my sister also joins the class
We get a lot of tourists who come here just to dive..
Eggplant lasagna is delicious and its really easy to bake. I make them pretty often..
I put out my old sewing machine for the community to use. Its never to late to learn a new skill..
Its Sunday again. Kids are back to school tomorrow..
The inn isnt crowded, but we have a few regulars..
Alice took a neuroscience class on zombies, where they try to map their hypothetical brain through a behavioral study and compare them to human's brain.
Of course it isnt real. Dont be silly! She also took an astrobiology class on the search for extraterrestrial life. I dont know what she was thinking..
I partied my years in university..
Ah I might go mini-golf tomorrow, hopefully Ben is in town. He's a great competitor to have
Alice takes care of the Inn in the morning usually, then I take over at 5ish..
Ive been wearing my hair purple as long as I can remember. If Alice didnt keep hers natural, I probably wouldve forgotten what my hair color actually is.
Do you wear a hat when you farm?
My sister and I may look alike, but we are 2 very different personalities..
I used to always get us in trouble, growing up. Ha ha ha
I hope Pufferfish stops their drilling practice, not just here but change business direction altogether..
Far-fetched, I know..
Her father and I instill the love of physical activities from a young age. We think its important for kids to keep active.
You must get your daily work-out from farming huh..
The Inn can get pretty messy sometimes, because Macy has a lobster tank in her room.
But she is nursing it back to health. So we are supportive of her good nature.
The air smells sticky today..
My ex' cousin, Rafael, helps us around the Inn with some handywork when he comes to visit Valentina on Sundays.
My parents are religious. They believe in Boda and still practicing until now..
A lot of cleaning up to do today..
Thats what the weekend is for.. Heh heh heh
Player! Im not sure if you remember me. Im Suki.. How was the farm so far?
Oh! Of course. I hope you like it here..
Thats good to hear! That lot has been empty for a while, its great that someones taking care of it.
Anyway, visit Sam if you havent already, to get more seeds for your farm. He only sells in-season seeds though.
Quite a party last night yah...
I dont think I had enough sleep. I still feel very sleepy..
Its Joko's birthday tomorrow. Should I get him some pineapples or a jar of yogurt?
Yeah, I think he would really appreciate it
Okay. It is a healthy snack..
I expect more rain than this..
Quite a name youve got, Player. Is there a meaning behind it?
My parents never explained why they named me Suki
I brought some squid and red spinach that I scavanged in the winter.
The weather is perfect for a picnic today!
I ate so much yesterday at cherry blossom festival, I think Im still a bit full today. Hah hah hah
I carry around extra sunscreen, if you need..
The beach gets dirty fast during Summer. Thankfully we have that annual beach clean up.
Beach clean up is an awesome thing, but we must also remember to use less plastic and recycle
I get my fresh flowers from Ben. He gives the Inn discount when we buy in bulk.
Im only here to pick up some irises from Ben for the Inn.
Im glad to see you taking a break from farming! Lets start the festival and get to dancing already!
The sun sure is shinning today.. Be sure to hydrate often okay.
A lot of people are so dedicated to this island. It was a great sight to see all of us together yesterday..
Its starting to get chilly at night..
Make sure to bring your best produces for mooncake festival on the 15th.
You can put some fish on your booth. I heard that it might increase your chance of winning..
But pumpkin is great too. Whats Fall without pumpkin, right?
I cant wait for Winter..
I thought it started to snow last night. I was so excited..
Im looking forward to see Taco tomorrow.. That puppy gets so excited to see other animals
Taco is so fluffy!
The competition today is not a "race", its just a fun activity on how we can bond with our pets.
Its Alice and my birthday month.. We share the same birthday. Surprise!
What should I cook for tomorrow?! If I couldnt settle on something, Im going to skip this year's cooking competition.
No big deal..
Everything smells so good! They should add a potluck session after cooking competition, dont you think?
Alice thinks that hot air balloon ride is very romantic, in case you were interested. Heh heh heh
Dont tell her I said that. Heh heh
Im staying put today..
The stew smells delicious. Its the perfect meal for this chilly weather..
Animals can have positive effects in our mental health
Are you going to Bree's dinner party on the 28th? I dont know if I should bring wine or something..
Im not too worried about Valentina, she knows how to be more careful when the ground is slippery.
Her father takes her climbing all the time. She's good at it.
Valentina likes to give me hard time when it comes to bed time..
It gets a bit cold in here, eh..
I wish the school would give the kids day off on stormy days like this.
Careful on your way home okay, Player.
Take the garden lane route tonight, will you. It might be safer than going through the lookout.
Well I just thought, it might be more slipery..
We need to find out how to crank up the heat in here..
The snow is getting thicker outside..
Winter is my favorite season and days like these are precisely why.
Alice and I grew up here. I remember playing around here.. Building snowman.
Great memories all around.
*dum dum dum* *dum*
Oh here, let me show you how to make green smoothies. Its so delicious and power drink..
Its a bit stuffy here. We need to open more windows..
You should take a break from farm life and stay here for a weekend or something..
You can just relax, read a book in your room, with an opened window. Falling asleep to calming sounds of wave..
We will give you discount. He heh heh
We have plenty amount of books in our library. They are well-read..
We have this system that guests are welcome to take the book that they are reading, in exchange for another book.
Take a book, leave a book thing.. If they dont have any books, its okay too. They dont have to leave anything.
You should check out the pier. There are usually so many seals out at this time..
Valentina needs to clean up that room of hers, or shes not sufring tomorrow.
Ah just dropping off Valentina..
What are you doing here so early in the morning?
Going fishing, Player?
I wish someone would just fix that broken piano already.. it isnt the prettiest sight
neglected like that..
Breath in.... Breath out....
Im going to clean up some of spider web after this.
Picking up some fresh fruits and veggies for dinner.
Flowers are a bit expensive here. So I usually get them from Ben instead.
Flowers are a bit expensive here. So I usually get them from Ben instead.
Im feeling good today. Im bringing my A game. Ha ha ha
Come here to play?
I think that mini golf that Pufferfish built is a great addition to our town..
She and I grow up together here..
Nina..
Thank you for this! It will make a very fresh green smoothies. Maybe one day I can share my recipe with you.
So, how much do I owe you?
